## OutgoingSubscribeRequestDelegate.onNotifyTimeout() method

Timed out waiting to receive the initial subscription creating NOTIFY in response to this request. Called for out of dialog SUBSCRIBE requests only (not called for re-SUBSCRIBE requests).

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
onNotifyTimeout?(): void;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

`void`
